1
00:00:20,770 --> 00:00:21,604
Hei!

2
00:00:22,105 --> 00:00:23,732
Kenapa kau di sini?

3
00:00:24,691 --> 00:00:25,984
Maaf.

4
00:00:26,693 --> 00:00:28,987
- Dari belakang mirip temanku.
- Ayo pergi.

5
00:00:29,070 --> 00:00:31,114
- Yang lain sudah berkumpul.
- Apa?

6
00:00:32,949 --> 00:00:33,867
Tunggu…

7
00:00:34,576 --> 00:00:35,410
Kenapa pergi?

8
00:00:37,662 --> 00:00:38,621
Bukan dia?

9
00:00:38,705 --> 00:00:39,539
Sial.

10
00:00:39,622 --> 00:00:42,083
Mi-rae!

11
00:00:43,168 --> 00:00:44,461
Sekretaris Choi…

12
00:00:45,086 --> 00:00:45,920
Apa?

13
00:00:46,004 --> 00:00:47,672
<i>Su-ji, teman kuliah.</i>

14
00:00:48,256 --> 00:00:49,090
Apa-apaan?

15
00:00:49,883 --> 00:00:52,343
Aku masih bingung
karena kampus kita luas.

16
00:00:52,427 --> 00:00:55,138
Aku hampir tak menemukanmu
setelah dari toilet.

17
00:00:55,221 --> 00:00:56,056
Ayo pergi.

18
00:00:57,015 --> 00:00:58,391
- Ke mana?
- Apa?

19
00:00:58,892 --> 00:01:00,185
Kita janji mau lihat-lihat.

20
00:01:01,436 --> 00:01:02,479
Ke sana.

21
00:01:05,815 --> 00:01:07,400
Ini tempatnya!

22
00:01:07,484 --> 00:01:08,651
FESTIVAL PEMUDA HANSAE

23
00:01:08,735 --> 00:01:09,569
Seru, ya?

24
00:01:09,652 --> 00:01:10,779
Apa? Mahasiswa baru?

25
00:01:10,862 --> 00:01:12,530
SELAMAT DATANG, MAHASISWA BARU

26
00:01:12,614 --> 00:01:15,116
<i>Aku bukan mahasiswa baru, 'kan?</i>

27
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:16,409
Tidak mungkin.

28
00:01:16,493 --> 00:01:18,536
- Silakan sweternya.
- Ini berapa?

29
00:01:18,620 --> 00:01:19,579
Cantik sekali.

30
00:01:20,080 --> 00:01:21,623
Aku boleh minta ini?

31
00:01:21,706 --> 00:01:22,540
Terima kasih.

32
00:01:23,917 --> 00:01:26,169
- Oi, Mahasiswa Baru!
- Mi-rae, aku dapat ini.

33
00:01:49,651 --> 00:01:51,319
<i>Menyebalkan sekali.</i>

34
00:01:57,784 --> 00:01:59,661
Ayo pergi. Aku tidak suka.

35
00:01:59,744 --> 00:02:01,162
Tak mau yang dekat saja?

36
00:02:01,663 --> 00:02:02,497
Tidak mau.

37
00:02:02,580 --> 00:02:04,791
- Bukan kau!
- Pergilah!

38
00:02:05,750 --> 00:02:08,002
- Ayo lihat-lihat!
- Lihat yang seru.

39
00:02:08,086 --> 00:02:10,046
- Banyak yang menarik.
- Semoga tertarik.

40
00:02:10,130 --> 00:02:11,589
- Ayo kemari.
- Ayo mampir.

41
00:02:11,673 --> 00:02:13,007
Ada yang seru di sini.

42
00:02:13,091 --> 00:02:15,009
Mohon perhatiannya!

43
00:02:15,593 --> 00:02:16,678
Ayo lihat-lihat.

44
00:02:16,761 --> 00:02:18,388
- Lihat kamera.
- Coba menendang!

45
00:02:18,471 --> 00:02:20,640
- Silakan ambil foto.
- Aku fotokan.

46
00:02:20,723 --> 00:02:23,143
Kenapa di sini antreannya panjang sekali?

47
00:02:23,226 --> 00:02:24,227
Hei!

48
00:02:24,310 --> 00:02:26,604
Dari tadi kenapa bicaramu kaku sekali?

49
00:02:29,399 --> 00:02:32,318
Benar sekali. Aku aneh sekali!

50
00:02:33,736 --> 00:02:37,323
Sepertinya itu antrean tiket
untuk pertandingan kumdo.

51
00:02:37,407 --> 00:02:40,034
Kudengar di toilet, tiketnya sudah habis.

52
00:02:40,535 --> 00:02:42,829
Apa masih ada pembatalan tiket?

53
00:02:42,912 --> 00:02:45,290
Klub kumdo tampaknya sangat populer.

54
00:02:45,790 --> 00:02:49,419
Ya. Mereka lebih terkenal
dibanding klub sepak bola dan hoki.

55
00:02:49,919 --> 00:02:51,588
PERTANDINGAN PERSAHABATAN KUMDO

56
00:02:51,671 --> 00:02:53,882
Luar biasa! Kau punya ini?

57
00:02:53,965 --> 00:02:56,176
Kau dapat dari mana? Gila sekali!

58
00:02:56,259 --> 00:02:58,094
Pasti aku disuruh ke sini, ya?

59
00:02:59,053 --> 00:03:00,388
Tentu harus pergi.

60
00:03:01,472 --> 00:03:02,432
Ayo ikut aku.

61
00:03:02,515 --> 00:03:03,850
Lewat sini.

62
00:03:22,535 --> 00:03:23,620
Dia datang!

63
00:03:23,703 --> 00:03:25,330
HANSAE VS KOSAN

64
00:03:26,706 --> 00:03:27,540
Ada apa?

65
00:03:28,750 --> 00:03:30,543
Jangan memfoto di sini!

66
00:03:30,627 --> 00:03:31,836
Memang kenapa?

67
00:03:31,920 --> 00:03:33,588
Kau menghalangi orang!

68
00:03:33,671 --> 00:03:35,632
- Sial.
- "Sial"?

69
00:03:36,341 --> 00:03:38,885
Siapa mereka? Klub penggemar seseorang?

70
00:03:38,968 --> 00:03:40,053
Tampaknya begitu.

71
00:03:40,136 --> 00:03:43,264
Pertandingan persahabatan
antara Hansae dan Kosan segera dimulai.

72
00:03:43,348 --> 00:03:48,978
Universitas Hansae!

73
00:03:49,062 --> 00:03:54,943
- Universitas Hansae!
- Universitas Kosan!

74
00:03:55,026 --> 00:03:55,860
Mulai!

75
00:03:59,364 --> 00:04:00,698
Kepala.

76
00:04:00,782 --> 00:04:01,950
Kepala!

77
00:04:08,665 --> 00:04:09,624
Kak Eun-ho!

78
00:04:20,426 --> 00:04:24,639
- Seo Eun-ho dari Univ. Hansae menang.
- Kak Eun-ho!

79
00:04:24,722 --> 00:04:28,559
Pertandingan selanjutnya mempertemukan
Park Myeong-seong dari Universitas Hansae

80
00:04:28,643 --> 00:04:31,854
dan An Hong-mo dari Universitas Kosan.

81
00:04:31,938 --> 00:04:33,564
Dimohon untuk tetap duduk.

82
00:04:35,566 --> 00:04:36,776
Pertandingan luar biasa.

83
00:04:45,493 --> 00:04:46,619
Kerennya!

84
00:04:46,703 --> 00:04:47,704
Kak Eun-ho!

85
00:04:47,787 --> 00:04:49,914
- Dia?
- Keren sekali.

86
00:04:50,707 --> 00:04:52,333
Dia sangat keren.

87
00:05:06,222 --> 00:05:10,018
<i>Selamat, Seo Mi-rae.</i>
<i>Kau telah bertemu pria kedua.</i>

88
00:05:20,486 --> 00:05:21,487
Sudah kuduga.

89
00:05:22,196 --> 00:05:23,281
Kau orangnya.

90
00:05:29,370 --> 00:05:33,833
EPISODE 3
MEMAHAMI CINTA PERTAMA

91
00:05:37,003 --> 00:05:38,046
KLUB KUMDO HANSAE

92
00:05:38,129 --> 00:05:40,423
Kalian mendaftar karena Kak Eun-ho?

93
00:05:40,506 --> 00:05:41,341
Tidak.

94
00:05:42,633 --> 00:05:43,551
Tidak apa-apa.

95
00:05:43,634 --> 00:05:45,178
Itu alasan kami juga.

96
00:05:45,678 --> 00:05:47,805
Kalian ingin dekat dengannya, ya?

97
00:05:47,889 --> 00:05:49,474
Ya.

98
00:05:49,557 --> 00:05:51,642
Kalau begitu, singkirkan kami dulu.

99
00:05:56,939 --> 00:05:59,317
Apakah Kak Eun-ho sepopuler itu?

100
00:05:59,400 --> 00:06:01,778
- Astaga.
- Apa menurutmu tak populer?

101
00:06:01,861 --> 00:06:04,364
Para mahasiswi ingin
dia terus di sini.

102
00:06:04,447 --> 00:06:08,326
Mengambil gelar sarjana, doktor,
dan jadi profesor di sini.

103
00:06:08,826 --> 00:06:11,162
Untung jurusan arsitektur lima tahun.

104
00:06:11,245 --> 00:06:15,375
Bukan pendidikan jasmani? Keren.
Dia jurusan arsitektur. Pasti pintar!

105
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:19,629
Kak Eun-ho tak hanya membangun gedung,
tapi membangun negara!

106
00:06:20,213 --> 00:06:21,172
Itu benar.

107
00:06:21,756 --> 00:06:24,967
<i>Pria paling populer di kampus menyukaiku?</i>

108
00:06:26,719 --> 00:06:28,429
<i>- Konsep yang bagus.</i>
- Kenapa tertawa?

109
00:06:29,305 --> 00:06:30,139
Apa?

110
00:06:32,725 --> 00:06:34,060
Tidak ada apa-apa.

111
00:06:37,772 --> 00:06:38,940
Perkenalan diri?

112
00:06:42,777 --> 00:06:46,072
<i>Aku mahasiswa baru, Seo Mi-rae.</i>
<i>Mohon bimbingannya.</i>

113
00:06:55,706 --> 00:06:56,958
<i>Ini di mana?</i>

114
00:06:58,876 --> 00:07:00,044
Tampannya.

115
00:07:00,128 --> 00:07:03,214
Mahasiswa Baru,
ini pertemuan pertama, 'kan?

116
00:07:03,714 --> 00:07:04,549
Beri salam.

117
00:07:05,133 --> 00:07:06,342
Halo.

118
00:07:06,426 --> 00:07:08,094
Halo.

119
00:07:11,514 --> 00:07:12,598
Hei.

120
00:07:12,682 --> 00:07:14,058
Kenapa kau di sini?

121
00:07:16,144 --> 00:07:18,312
<i>Dia yang tadi…</i>

122
00:07:18,396 --> 00:07:21,190
Hei. Ketua klub sangat cantik, ya?

123
00:07:22,483 --> 00:07:23,568
Kau benar.

124
00:07:41,586 --> 00:07:45,214
Kumdo adalah olahraga terbaik
untuk melatih tubuh dan pikiran.

125
00:07:45,298 --> 00:07:46,466
Di klub ini,

126
00:07:46,549 --> 00:07:50,219
kalian akan diajarkan
mulai dari gerakan dasar sampai sparing.

127
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:54,348
Ini hari pertama, jadi kita akan mulai
dari langkah dasar.

128
00:07:55,349 --> 00:07:56,601
Ada yang mengajukan diri?

129
00:07:57,268 --> 00:07:58,644
Ada yang mau coba?

130
00:08:07,528 --> 00:08:08,446
Ya!

131
00:08:08,529 --> 00:08:09,405
Kau, majulah.

132
00:08:10,031 --> 00:08:10,865
Apa?

133
00:08:12,617 --> 00:08:14,744
Oh, bukan begitu.

134
00:08:14,827 --> 00:08:16,204
- Bukan.
- Majulah. Tak apa.

135
00:08:16,287 --> 00:08:17,163
Ayo maju.

136
00:08:22,043 --> 00:08:23,377
Siapa namamu?

137
00:08:23,461 --> 00:08:26,047
Aku Seo Mi-rae.

138
00:08:32,386 --> 00:08:35,806
Aku berharap ada yang bisa membantu.

139
00:08:38,392 --> 00:08:40,186
Ya. Tolong bantu.

140
00:08:40,269 --> 00:08:42,939
Lagi pula, mereka datang untuk melihatmu.

141
00:08:44,774 --> 00:08:45,608
Begitu?

142
00:08:49,070 --> 00:08:50,196
Kau tak masalah?

143
00:08:51,989 --> 00:08:52,823
Ya.

144
00:08:59,872 --> 00:09:00,706
Hai.

145
00:09:02,250 --> 00:09:03,668
Halo, Kak.

146
00:09:03,751 --> 00:09:05,294
Pernah coba kumdo?

147
00:09:06,712 --> 00:09:07,838
Tidak pernah.

148
00:09:13,261 --> 00:09:14,095
Pegang ini.

149
00:09:16,931 --> 00:09:18,349
Pegang seperti ini.

150
00:09:19,433 --> 00:09:20,935
Kaki kanan ke depan.

151
00:09:24,063 --> 00:09:25,481
Bagaimana? Nyaman?

152
00:09:26,732 --> 00:09:27,567
Ya.

153
00:09:29,277 --> 00:09:30,403
Ini kuda-kuda atas,

154
00:09:32,280 --> 00:09:33,322
serangan kepala,

155
00:09:33,406 --> 00:09:35,032
dan ini kuda-kuda tengah.

156
00:09:35,658 --> 00:09:37,743
Sikap dasar selalu di tengah.

157
00:09:37,827 --> 00:09:38,869
Mau mencobanya?

158
00:09:40,246 --> 00:09:41,080
Ya.

159
00:09:47,253 --> 00:09:48,087
Cobalah.

160
00:09:50,506 --> 00:09:51,340
Kepala.

161
00:09:57,346 --> 00:09:58,180
Astaga.

162
00:10:00,016 --> 00:10:01,225
Apa-apaan?

163
00:10:02,268 --> 00:10:06,105
- Benar tak pernah coba kumdo?
- Ini pertama kalinya.

164
00:10:07,481 --> 00:10:09,442
<i>Apa? Kenapa begini?</i>

165
00:10:10,026 --> 00:10:11,527
<i>Padahal badanku kaku.</i>

166
00:10:13,738 --> 00:10:15,656
Ternyata kau sangat atletis, ya?

167
00:10:15,740 --> 00:10:17,033
Ayo coba sekali lagi.

168
00:10:18,951 --> 00:10:19,785
Baik.

169
00:10:59,116 --> 00:11:00,993
Sampai tak kelihatan. Sayang sekali.

170
00:11:01,077 --> 00:11:02,912
- Apa itu?
- Tak kelihatan.

171
00:11:02,995 --> 00:11:04,163
Luar biasa.

172
00:11:04,830 --> 00:11:07,375
Mi-rae, kau sangat berbakat.

173
00:11:07,458 --> 00:11:10,878
- Jelas Kak Eun-ho mengalah kepadanya.
- Tidak.

174
00:11:12,630 --> 00:11:13,589
Kerja bagus.

175
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:16,175
Kunantikan permainanmu lagi.

176
00:11:18,719 --> 00:11:19,553
Baik.

177
00:11:21,138 --> 00:11:21,972
Kepala!

178
00:11:22,056 --> 00:11:23,182
- Kepala!
- Kepala!

179
00:11:24,016 --> 00:11:25,351
- Satu.
- Kerennya.

180
00:11:25,851 --> 00:11:27,269
- Benar.
- Kepala!

181
00:11:27,353 --> 00:11:29,188
- Gerakannya stabil.
- Tengah!

182
00:11:29,271 --> 00:11:30,481
Fisiknya…

183
00:11:30,564 --> 00:11:33,192
- Fisiknya luar biasa!
- Memang!

184
00:11:33,818 --> 00:11:35,361
Seperti berjalan. Perhatikan.

185
00:11:35,444 --> 00:11:36,320
Satu!

186
00:11:36,404 --> 00:11:37,321
Kepala!

187
00:11:38,364 --> 00:11:39,573
Bagus.

188
00:11:41,117 --> 00:11:42,410
Pak Ko?

189
00:11:42,493 --> 00:11:43,369
Apa?

190
00:11:43,953 --> 00:11:44,995
Oh, itu…

191
00:11:51,585 --> 00:11:54,463
Kenapa kalian diam saja? Ada masalah?

192
00:11:55,673 --> 00:11:57,341
<i>Jung-pil, senior klub kumdo.</i>

193
00:11:58,008 --> 00:11:59,009
Oh, itu…

194
00:11:59,885 --> 00:12:00,720
Siapa namamu?

195
00:12:01,887 --> 00:12:02,722
Aku Su-ji.

196
00:12:02,805 --> 00:12:03,931
- Su-ji?
- Ya.

197
00:12:04,014 --> 00:12:05,683
- Su-ji, kemarilah.
- Baik.

198
00:12:06,350 --> 00:12:09,562
Inti dari kumdo adalah gerakan lembut.

199
00:12:09,645 --> 00:12:10,855
Kepala!

200
00:12:11,564 --> 00:12:12,481
Kepala!

201
00:12:13,023 --> 00:12:14,734
- Sangat lembut.
- Cobalah.

202
00:12:17,403 --> 00:12:18,529
Kepala!

203
00:12:19,029 --> 00:12:20,948
Ketua, perhatikan mereka.

204
00:12:21,031 --> 00:12:22,158
Baiklah.

205
00:12:22,241 --> 00:12:23,576
Kepala!

206
00:12:27,788 --> 00:12:28,622
Kak Eun-ho!

207
00:12:31,625 --> 00:12:32,460
Mau ke mana?

208
00:12:33,043 --> 00:12:34,378
Perpustakaan. Kenapa?

209
00:12:35,880 --> 00:12:37,923
Kau mau makan bersamaku?

210
00:12:39,091 --> 00:12:40,092
Dengan yang lain?

211
00:12:41,761 --> 00:12:42,595
Tidak.

212
00:12:43,721 --> 00:12:44,930
Hanya kita berdua?

213
00:12:45,598 --> 00:12:46,432
Ya.

214
00:12:49,852 --> 00:12:51,729
Kau tipe yang agresif, ya.

215
00:12:52,438 --> 00:12:53,731
- Apa?
- Lain kali.

216
00:12:54,315 --> 00:12:55,316
Kalau sudah akrab.

217
00:12:56,275 --> 00:12:57,610
- Apa?
- Hati-hati di jalan.

218
00:12:58,986 --> 00:13:00,905
Kak Eun-ho!

219
00:13:00,988 --> 00:13:02,072
Hei, Seo Eun-ho.

220
00:13:03,574 --> 00:13:05,242
Mau ke mana? Ayo pergi bersama.

221
00:13:05,326 --> 00:13:06,869
- Ayo kita makan.
- Ya.

222
00:13:11,499 --> 00:13:13,501
Bukankah kau jatuh cinta kepadaku?

223
00:13:13,584 --> 00:13:14,877
<i>Kenapa harus begitu?</i>

224
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:18,005
Tentu dia harus menyukaiku.
Ini Boyfriend on Demand.

225
00:13:18,506 --> 00:13:21,425
Tampaknya kau salah paham.

226
00:13:21,509 --> 00:13:22,343
Salah paham?

227
00:13:23,385 --> 00:13:25,471
Jadi, kaukira 900 orang di sini

228
00:13:25,554 --> 00:13:27,807
harus mengejar-ngejarmu sejak awal?

229
00:13:29,642 --> 00:13:31,268
Tapi…

230
00:13:35,189 --> 00:13:36,690
Choi Si-woo sejak awal…

231
00:13:36,774 --> 00:13:40,152
Skenario Choi Si-woo memang seperti itu.

232
00:13:43,155 --> 00:13:46,992
Tak kusangka, ternyata kau
merasa seperti tuan putri.

233
00:13:47,827 --> 00:13:51,539
Jadi, Seo Eun-ho mungkin
tak akan menyukaiku sampai akhir?

234
00:13:51,622 --> 00:13:52,873
Tak ada yang tahu.

235
00:13:53,541 --> 00:13:55,543
Setiap pria punya tantangan berbeda.

236
00:13:56,293 --> 00:13:59,922
Kalau harus berusaha begitu,
sama seperti di kehidupan nyata.

237
00:14:00,005 --> 00:14:01,674
Jika tak suka Eun-ho, mau pria lain?

238
00:14:02,633 --> 00:14:03,676
Lewati saja?

239
00:14:07,680 --> 00:14:09,265
Tunggu!

240
00:14:09,348 --> 00:14:10,349
Tunggu sebentar.

241
00:14:10,432 --> 00:14:12,601
Kalau tak suka, lewati saja.

242
00:14:12,685 --> 00:14:13,769
Kau tak ada waktu.

243
00:14:13,853 --> 00:14:15,729
Ya, waktu…

244
00:14:16,772 --> 00:14:17,606
Waktu?

245
00:14:29,994 --> 00:14:30,828
Astaga.

246
00:14:44,133 --> 00:14:45,259
Kyeong-nam.

247
00:14:46,677 --> 00:14:47,636
Yang benar saja.

248
00:14:51,473 --> 00:14:52,308
Mau kopi?

249
00:14:52,391 --> 00:14:55,185
Episode pertama <i>PlanC </i>bagus juga, ya?

250
00:15:00,608 --> 00:15:01,984
Bu Yun cukup berat, ya?

251
00:15:03,235 --> 00:15:04,778
Aku sudah tahu sejak awal.

252
00:15:05,362 --> 00:15:07,990
Serius kau mau ke hari Jumat?

253
00:15:08,073 --> 00:15:08,908
Tidak.

254
00:15:10,618 --> 00:15:11,994
Seo Mi-rae tak akan setuju.

255
00:15:12,578 --> 00:15:14,830
Tentu tidak. Dia benci denganku.

256
00:15:16,457 --> 00:15:17,291
Kau tak benci?

257
00:15:27,551 --> 00:15:28,385
Hei.

258
00:15:29,929 --> 00:15:30,846
Ya, Pak.

259
00:15:32,556 --> 00:15:33,390
Masuklah.

260
00:15:37,853 --> 00:15:39,229
Kau memanggilku, Pak?

261
00:15:41,065 --> 00:15:42,316
Bu Yun baru meneleponku.

262
00:15:43,484 --> 00:15:44,860
Apa? Ada apa?

263
00:15:44,944 --> 00:15:47,446
Apa lagi alasannya meneleponku?

264
00:15:49,657 --> 00:15:53,369
Sejujurnya aku mau berhenti.
Aku muak dengan semua ini.

265
00:15:53,452 --> 00:15:55,871
Tolong selamatkan aku. Oke?

266
00:15:59,959 --> 00:16:01,126
Apa dia bilang

267
00:16:01,835 --> 00:16:03,003
mau berhenti?

268
00:16:03,087 --> 00:16:04,004
Dia mau berhenti?

269
00:16:04,088 --> 00:16:05,255
- Ya?
- Apa?

270
00:16:06,048 --> 00:16:07,466
- Tidak.
- Dasar kau ini.

271
00:16:08,258 --> 00:16:09,259
Lalu, kenapa…

272
00:16:10,344 --> 00:16:14,348
Dia minta libur dua minggu,
kalau tak mau dia mati di akhir pekan.

273
00:16:14,848 --> 00:16:17,226
Bu Yun sangat bekerja keras kali ini.

274
00:16:18,769 --> 00:16:19,603
Kerja bagus.

275
00:16:20,938 --> 00:16:23,565
- Ya?
- Bagus. Teruslah begini.

276
00:16:24,608 --> 00:16:27,069
Kau hebat. Kenapa merengek terus?

277
00:16:27,152 --> 00:16:30,322
Sementara Bu Yun libur,
siapkan rencana selanjutnya.

278
00:16:31,991 --> 00:16:34,076
Kau mengizinkannya hiatus?

279
00:16:35,911 --> 00:16:38,580
- Sudah lama tak main di hari kerja!
- Harum sekali.

280
00:16:38,664 --> 00:16:39,498
Cepat masuk.

281
00:16:41,333 --> 00:16:43,627
Jadi, kau senggang selama dua minggu?

282
00:16:43,711 --> 00:16:45,337
Mau ke Jeju akhir pekan?

283
00:16:45,421 --> 00:16:47,464
Hei, mana bisa ke Jeju?

284
00:16:47,548 --> 00:16:50,134
Aku harus mengurus penulis lain.
Aku tak senggang.

285
00:16:50,217 --> 00:16:52,094
Sejak dulu aku merasa

286
00:16:52,177 --> 00:16:55,139
pekerjaanmu sebagai produser tak sepadan.

287
00:16:55,222 --> 00:16:56,473
Memang tak sepadan.

288
00:16:57,433 --> 00:16:58,517
Kelihatan enak!

289
00:17:01,645 --> 00:17:02,896
Hei, Lee Ji-yeon.

290
00:17:02,980 --> 00:17:06,900
Seandainya kau bisa kembali
ke usia 20 tahun,

291
00:17:07,484 --> 00:17:08,318
mau melakukan apa?

292
00:17:12,948 --> 00:17:13,782
Bercinta.

293
00:17:16,368 --> 00:17:17,536
Bukan seperti itu.

294
00:17:19,621 --> 00:17:20,456
Memang kenapa?

295
00:17:20,539 --> 00:17:22,750
Mau apa kalau kau kembali ke usia 20?

296
00:17:24,334 --> 00:17:25,169
Aku ingin

297
00:17:25,252 --> 00:17:27,963
menjalani hidup
yang berbeda dari sekarang.

298
00:17:28,047 --> 00:17:29,048
Kebalikannya.

299
00:17:29,131 --> 00:17:31,091
- "Kebalikan"?
- Ya.

300
00:17:31,175 --> 00:17:32,426
Seperti itu.

301
00:17:32,509 --> 00:17:34,970
Jika ada yang kutaksir,
langsung kudekati.

302
00:17:35,054 --> 00:17:36,430
Apa pun yang terjadi,

303
00:17:37,056 --> 00:17:41,101
aku akan melakukan semuanya
dengan lebih agresif.

304
00:17:43,771 --> 00:17:46,732
Hei, kau lucu sekali.

305
00:17:46,815 --> 00:17:47,733
Apanya?

306
00:17:47,816 --> 00:17:51,111
Saat 20 tahun, kau sangat agresif.

307
00:17:51,195 --> 00:17:52,029
Aku?

308
00:17:52,112 --> 00:17:53,155
Ya!

309
00:17:54,740 --> 00:17:56,825
Kim Se-june itu suka Na You-mi,

310
00:17:56,909 --> 00:18:00,245
tapi kau menggoyahkan hatinya
dan berhasil jadi pacarmu.

311
00:18:02,414 --> 00:18:03,916
Kau lupa, ya?

312
00:18:05,292 --> 00:18:08,420
Padahal You-mi sangat populer saat itu.

313
00:18:09,213 --> 00:18:11,381
Meski tidak sepopuler aku.

314
00:18:13,550 --> 00:18:14,468
Kau benar.

315
00:18:14,968 --> 00:18:16,345
Dulu aku seperti itu.

316
00:18:19,848 --> 00:18:21,391
Kenapa sekarang aku begini?

317
00:18:22,476 --> 00:18:25,604
Mungkin berubah karena kalian
sudah lama pacaran.

318
00:18:26,271 --> 00:18:27,272
Sudah tambah tua juga.

319
00:18:27,856 --> 00:18:29,233
Di masa-masa awal,

320
00:18:30,109 --> 00:18:32,653
rasanya hubunganku dan Se-june
sangat manis.

321
00:18:34,488 --> 00:18:36,281
Ya, benar sekali.

322
00:18:36,824 --> 00:18:38,534
Aku juga iri dengan kalian.

323
00:18:47,209 --> 00:18:48,794
<i>Seo Eun-ho itu…</i>

324
00:18:49,711 --> 00:18:51,380
<i>tingkat kesulitannya tinggi.</i>

325
00:18:53,215 --> 00:18:56,385
<i>Saat 20 tahun, kau sangat agresif.</i>

326
00:18:59,596 --> 00:19:01,014
Apa kucoba saja?

327
00:19:01,598 --> 00:19:03,934
Dalam arsitektur klasik,

328
00:19:04,017 --> 00:19:08,272
kuil diklasifikasikan berdasarkan
jumlah kolom bagian depan dan belakang.

329
00:19:09,064 --> 00:19:11,567
Jika ada dua kolom disebut <i>distyle</i>,

330
00:19:11,650 --> 00:19:13,944
empat kolom disebut <i>tetrastyle</i>,

331
00:19:14,027 --> 00:19:16,864
dan enam kolom disebut <i>hexastyle</i>.

332
00:19:17,364 --> 00:19:18,323
<i>Hexastyle </i>ini…

333
00:19:31,920 --> 00:19:32,921
Halo, Kak.

334
00:19:33,422 --> 00:19:34,256
Hai.

335
00:19:34,840 --> 00:19:37,301
- Boleh aku duduk di sini?
- Terserahmu.

336
00:19:41,930 --> 00:19:42,764
Bisa minggir?

337
00:19:43,724 --> 00:19:44,766
Tunggu sebentar.

338
00:19:54,318 --> 00:19:55,611
Silakan lewat.

339
00:19:59,531 --> 00:20:01,366
Mau terus bertingkah begitu?

340
00:20:03,202 --> 00:20:06,622
Kolom pada kuil juga bisa
diklasifikasikan dari bentuknya.

341
00:20:06,705 --> 00:20:12,127
<i>Karena tekadku sudah bulat,</i>
<i>aku keluarkan semua teknik lama.</i>

342
00:20:15,797 --> 00:20:17,049
Sudah sampai mana?

343
00:20:20,052 --> 00:20:22,471
Dikelompokkan menjadi <i>Doric </i>dan <i>Ionic</i>.

344
00:20:26,183 --> 00:20:27,643
Terima kasih.

345
00:20:39,488 --> 00:20:40,405
Maaf.

346
00:20:52,918 --> 00:20:53,752
Hei…

347
00:20:56,463 --> 00:20:57,297
Kenapa?

348
00:20:58,131 --> 00:20:59,466
Kau sedang sakit?

349
00:21:02,511 --> 00:21:03,345
Tidak.

350
00:21:04,137 --> 00:21:04,972
Oke.

351
00:21:05,681 --> 00:21:06,848
Ayo kita belajar.

352
00:21:19,903 --> 00:21:22,155
Kak, mau ke ruang latihan?

353
00:21:22,656 --> 00:21:23,865
Mau ke perpustakaan.

354
00:21:25,158 --> 00:21:27,119
Kebetulan. Aku mau ke sana juga.

355
00:21:27,202 --> 00:21:28,954
Baru ingat, aku ada latihan.

356
00:21:30,872 --> 00:21:32,416
Aku juga mau latihan.

357
00:22:00,068 --> 00:22:01,403
Mau mulai duluan?

358
00:22:30,474 --> 00:22:31,308
<i>Apa?</i>

359
00:22:33,518 --> 00:22:34,436
<i>Apa ini?</i>

360
00:22:35,562 --> 00:22:36,563
<i>Dia mulai menyukaiku?</i>

361
00:22:54,122 --> 00:22:55,540
Jangan sengaja mengalah…

362
00:22:58,960 --> 00:23:00,295
seperti waktu itu.

363
00:23:05,092 --> 00:23:06,385
Main dengan serius.

364
00:23:07,928 --> 00:23:08,762
<i>Gawat.</i>

365
00:23:11,973 --> 00:23:12,974
Pakailah.

366
00:23:20,482 --> 00:23:22,943
<i>Aku mencoreng harga dirinya.</i>

367
00:23:34,538 --> 00:23:36,039
Hai, Mi-rae.

368
00:23:36,623 --> 00:23:37,666
Halo, Kak.

369
00:23:39,000 --> 00:23:40,001
Ada apa?

370
00:23:40,752 --> 00:23:42,379
Kalian habis sparing?

371
00:23:43,713 --> 00:23:45,757
Oh, soal itu…

372
00:23:46,258 --> 00:23:47,175
Kak Eun-ho…

373
00:23:47,259 --> 00:23:48,468
Aku yang minta.

374
00:23:53,348 --> 00:23:54,307
Lalu?

375
00:23:54,391 --> 00:23:56,393
Bagaimana hasilnya?

376
00:24:00,272 --> 00:24:02,357
MI-RAE, EUN-HO

377
00:24:02,441 --> 00:24:04,860
<i>Katanya aku akan jadi ratu kampus.</i>

378
00:24:04,943 --> 00:24:06,695
<i>Aku malah dibuat jadi ahli pedang?</i>

379
00:24:06,778 --> 00:24:08,280
MI-RAE MENANG, EUN-HO KALAH

380
00:24:10,157 --> 00:24:11,366
Jangan bilang

381
00:24:11,867 --> 00:24:13,160
kalau kau kalah.

382
00:24:15,412 --> 00:24:17,497
Astaga, itu tak masuk akal.

383
00:24:18,874 --> 00:24:19,916
Serius?

384
00:24:22,711 --> 00:24:24,129
Aku pergi mandi dulu.

385
00:24:33,388 --> 00:24:34,681
Sial…

386
00:24:36,308 --> 00:24:37,809
Ayo!

387
00:24:41,438 --> 00:24:43,648
- Kelinci!
- Wortel!

388
00:24:43,732 --> 00:24:46,318
<i>Energi yang lama tak kurasakan ini.</i>

389
00:24:46,818 --> 00:24:48,028
<i>Semangat masa muda.</i>

390
00:24:48,111 --> 00:24:49,154
Wortel!

391
00:24:49,237 --> 00:24:50,697
Kelinci!

392
00:24:50,780 --> 00:24:52,115
Kelinci!

393
00:24:52,199 --> 00:24:53,408
Kelinci!

394
00:24:53,492 --> 00:24:55,410
Kelinci!

395
00:24:55,494 --> 00:24:56,953
Kau salah!

396
00:24:57,037 --> 00:24:59,998
Minumlah!

397
00:25:00,081 --> 00:25:01,124
Aku saja…

398
00:25:02,292 --> 00:25:03,210
Aku gantikan.

399
00:25:05,170 --> 00:25:07,714
- Hei, buat minuman hukuman.
- Minuman hukuman.

400
00:25:07,797 --> 00:25:08,882
Baik!

401
00:25:09,508 --> 00:25:10,675
Akan kusiapkan.

402
00:25:11,259 --> 00:25:12,677
- Mi-rae!
- Seo Mi-rae.

403
00:25:12,761 --> 00:25:13,762
Ya, cobalah.

404
00:25:16,389 --> 00:25:17,432
Akan kumulai.

405
00:25:20,810 --> 00:25:21,978
Pakai soju juga?

406
00:25:28,193 --> 00:25:30,487
Ini dia minuman hukumannya.

407
00:25:31,863 --> 00:25:33,615
Mi-rae, kau…

408
00:25:34,241 --> 00:25:35,075
Kenapa?

409
00:25:35,158 --> 00:25:36,535
Ada apa dengan hidupmu?

410
00:25:37,369 --> 00:25:38,495
<i>Semangatku terlalu</i>

411
00:25:39,204 --> 00:25:40,288
<i>berlebihan.</i>

412
00:25:40,372 --> 00:25:41,790
Apa begini caranya?

413
00:25:42,332 --> 00:25:43,583
Eun-ho!

414
00:25:43,667 --> 00:25:44,960
- Halo, Kak.
- Halo.

415
00:25:45,043 --> 00:25:46,586
- Halo, Kak.
- Duduklah.

416
00:25:47,754 --> 00:25:49,464
- Duduk di sini.
- Halo, Kak.

417
00:25:50,674 --> 00:25:52,050
Kenapa baru datang?

418
00:25:52,133 --> 00:25:53,343
- Ada tugas.
- Minumlah.

419
00:25:53,426 --> 00:25:55,387
Sekali teguk. Oke!

420
00:25:55,470 --> 00:25:57,222
Ini dia. Kau harus minum!

421
00:25:57,305 --> 00:25:58,265
Su-ji, hentikan.

422
00:25:59,474 --> 00:26:02,102
Tidak. Aku tahu kau tak bisa minum.

423
00:26:02,185 --> 00:26:03,228
Bersulang.

424
00:26:03,311 --> 00:26:04,563
Biar aku yang minum.

425
00:26:05,063 --> 00:26:06,731
<i>- Dasar.</i>
- Kau jangan minum.

426
00:26:06,815 --> 00:26:09,234
<i>Sejak awal aku tak menyukainya.</i>

427
00:26:09,776 --> 00:26:11,903
<i>Anehnya, dia mirip Na You-mi.</i>

428
00:26:12,404 --> 00:26:13,697
Ada sesuatu di sini.

429
00:26:14,990 --> 00:26:15,824
Kak Jung-pil.

430
00:26:16,491 --> 00:26:18,326
Tidak. Jangan memaksakan diri.

431
00:26:18,868 --> 00:26:20,704
Besok perutmu bisa sakit.

432
00:26:21,871 --> 00:26:24,708
Mi-rae, apa kau memang
menggeluti olahraga?

433
00:26:26,459 --> 00:26:27,502
Tidak.

434
00:26:28,587 --> 00:26:30,005
Kau jurusan seni, ya?

435
00:26:30,088 --> 00:26:33,508
Kau jago melukis dan olahraga juga.
Itu tidak adil.

436
00:26:35,760 --> 00:26:38,013
Tidak begitu, Kak.

437
00:26:41,099 --> 00:26:43,059
Terlalu rendah hati juga bahaya.

438
00:26:44,561 --> 00:26:46,062
Ada apa denganmu?

439
00:26:46,563 --> 00:26:48,148
Rendah hati itu bagus.

440
00:26:48,648 --> 00:26:50,275
Benar kata Kak Eun-ho.

441
00:26:50,358 --> 00:26:53,903
Kalau terlalu bersikap begitu,
jadi terdengar menyebalkan.

442
00:26:53,987 --> 00:26:54,863
Sebal.

443
00:26:56,323 --> 00:26:57,324
Kak.

444
00:26:57,949 --> 00:26:59,993
- Apa?
- Bukan kau, Kak.

445
00:27:03,580 --> 00:27:04,497
Kau membenciku?

446
00:27:06,333 --> 00:27:07,250
- Apa?
- Apa?

447
00:27:12,547 --> 00:27:14,132
Aku tidak membenci orang.

448
00:27:15,759 --> 00:27:17,385
Maaf membuatmu salah paham.

449
00:27:21,389 --> 00:27:22,474
Syukurlah.

450
00:27:24,476 --> 00:27:26,144
- Hei, Mi-rae.
- Mi-rae.

451
00:27:26,227 --> 00:27:27,771
- Mau ke mana?
- Kenapa?

452
00:27:34,444 --> 00:27:36,821
Karena aku menyukaimu, Kak.

453
00:27:38,865 --> 00:27:40,408
- Apa?
- Dia sudah gila.

454
00:27:40,909 --> 00:27:43,620
- Apa-apaan?
- Dia jago sekali menggoda.

455
00:27:48,667 --> 00:27:50,460
Kita belum lama kenal.

456
00:27:51,294 --> 00:27:52,128
Apa?

457
00:27:53,254 --> 00:27:54,506
Kau belum mengenalku.

458
00:28:01,429 --> 00:28:04,015
Anak zaman sekarang
sangat berani dan hebat.

459
00:28:04,099 --> 00:28:06,518
Kak, ada yang menempel di sini.

460
00:28:06,601 --> 00:28:08,269
- Memalukan.
- Menempel ketampanan.

461
00:28:10,063 --> 00:28:11,147
- Ketampanan.
- Astaga.

462
00:28:11,231 --> 00:28:13,024
- Tunggu.
- Jangan ikut-ikutan.

463
00:28:13,108 --> 00:28:14,859
- Ayo bersulang.
- Oke, Kak.

464
00:28:14,943 --> 00:28:15,860
Menyebalkan.

465
00:28:18,405 --> 00:28:19,406
<i>Apa-apaan dia?</i>

466
00:28:19,489 --> 00:28:20,657
Kau terbaik bagiku.

467
00:28:20,740 --> 00:28:22,200
Sampai jumpa. Dah!

468
00:28:22,283 --> 00:28:24,035
- Su-ji, mau naik ini?
- Aku naik?

469
00:28:24,119 --> 00:28:25,286
Ya, naiklah.

470
00:28:25,829 --> 00:28:27,122
Terima kasih.

471
00:28:27,205 --> 00:28:28,665
Kak, cepat masuk.

472
00:28:49,352 --> 00:28:50,186
Kau mau ke mana?

473
00:28:51,104 --> 00:28:51,938
Ke kampus.

474
00:28:53,356 --> 00:28:54,858
Tinggal di asrama, ya?

475
00:28:56,443 --> 00:28:57,819
Kau ke kampus juga?

476
00:28:57,902 --> 00:29:00,363
Ya. Tugasku belum selesai,
jadi harus ke perpustakaan.

477
00:29:01,114 --> 00:29:02,073
Begitu, ya.

478
00:29:09,706 --> 00:29:11,666
Kalau ke kampus juga,
jalanlah di sampingku.

479
00:29:11,750 --> 00:29:13,918
Kau seperti mengejarku dari belakang.

480
00:29:22,010 --> 00:29:23,595
- Kak Eun-ho.
- Kenapa?

481
00:29:25,013 --> 00:29:26,431
Kau suka ketua klub kita?

482
00:29:27,474 --> 00:29:28,308
Apa?

483
00:29:31,102 --> 00:29:32,520
Apa aku terlalu tergesa-gesa?

484
00:29:33,813 --> 00:29:35,482
Kalau begitu, asalmu dari mana?

485
00:29:35,565 --> 00:29:36,524
Tipe idealmu?

486
00:29:37,025 --> 00:29:38,193
Apa kau suka gim?

487
00:29:38,860 --> 00:29:39,694
Kau kenapa?

488
00:29:41,154 --> 00:29:42,739
Kaubilang aku belum mengenalmu.

489
00:29:43,239 --> 00:29:44,783
Jadi, aku ingin segera mengenalmu.

490
00:29:55,168 --> 00:29:56,002
Kak Eun-ho.

491
00:29:59,756 --> 00:30:00,757
Ayo lari!

492
00:30:58,648 --> 00:31:00,942
Bagaimana bisa mengerjakan tugas
jika basah begitu?

493
00:31:01,025 --> 00:31:03,236
Ada baju kering di tasku. Tak masalah.

494
00:31:03,987 --> 00:31:05,613
Bajumu harus dikeringkan.

495
00:31:09,659 --> 00:31:10,660
ASRAMA HANSAE

496
00:31:10,743 --> 00:31:11,578
RUANG CUCI

